text: Korneliya Nikolaeva Naydenova (; born 1 February 1982) is a Bulgarian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper. She has been a member of the Bulgaria women's national team. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Bulgarian women's footballers Category:Bulgaria women's international footballers Category:FC NSA Sofia players
